NOTE ON DATA AND THIRD-PARTY ASSETS

This MIT license covers the source code in this repository. It does NOT relicense
third-party data or assets that the scripts download at runtime, which retain
their own licenses and terms, including but not limited to:

  - HCP-YA structural connectivity (via GNN_SC_FC / Human Connectome Project);
    HCP data use terms apply.
  - OpenNeuro ds003059 (Carhart-Harris et al. LSD fMRI); see the dataset license.
  - Schaefer 2018 parcellation and Yeo networks (ThomasYeoLab / CBIG).
  - fsLR-32k surfaces, parcellations, and eigenmode tooling (NSBLab/BrainEigenmodes).

Please consult and comply with each source's license before redistributing
derived data. Results in this repository are educational/research artifacts and
are group-average, parcellated, and not individual or clinical data.
